'''Juba''' (aka  ''"Joba")'' ndi pseudonym wa ananena [[Sniper]] nawo [[Iraq War|Iraq nkhondo]] 'm [[Iraqi insurgency (2003â€“11)|zigawenga]] , nkhani mavidiyo angapo.  Yachiwiri mwa mavidiyowa akuwonetsa Juba akudandaula kuti adaphera [[United States Armed Forces|asirikari]] 37 a ku [[United States Armed Forces|America]]. Kaya Juba ndi munthu weniweni, gawo lomwe amagawana ndi anthu angapo, kapena kufalitsa / kufalitsa nkhani sikudziwika. 

Juba anakhala wotchuka pambuyo pa luso lapadera lotha kuwombera linawonetsedwa m'mavidiyo a pa Intaneti omwe adatulutsidwa. 

Juba sniper mwachionekere ankagwira ntchito zambiri za Sunni zigawo za Iraq, makamaka chigawo cha [[Al Anbar Governorate|Anbar]] chomwe chinali chigawo chakupha kwambiri kwa asilikali a US pa nkhondo ya Iraq.  Mavidiyo a Juba anali otsika koma anasonyezanso masewero enieni a nkhondo ndi [[Nasheed|nasheeds]] .  M'makanema ambiri, Juba akuwoneka akupha asilikali ambiri a US ndi zomwe zikuoneka kuti ndi [[Dragunov sniper rifle|Dragunov]] , mfuti ya ku Russia.  Juba amawonedwa akupha mkati mwa mamita mazana angapo mpaka mamita chikwi osamvetseka mu mavidiyo otulutsidwa ndi molondola kwambiri. 

